data.description: West side 4+2 one story home in a highly recommended westside neighborhood featuring amenities with high end upgrades which include a master suite, walk-in closet, dual vanity sinks. The kitchen is adjacent to the family room leading to  new patio doors exposing a newer outdoor covered patio with lighting and ceiling fans, a huge living room, with lots of windows, a family room plus an indoor  laundry room leading to an oversized 2 car garage with a metal door and remote opener. Situated on  large lot with a tiled roof and newer solar system for efficiency. This neighborhood has great schools , shopping and transportation nearby. Buyers can also assume seller's FHA loan at 3.5%. Contact agent for details.
